  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Centre for Behavioural Studies - a research center which applies behavioural science approaches to address practical challenges and provides evidence-based solutions</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Apply behavioral science to improve policy and public services by working closely with departments within the government. &#x2022; Engage in specific projects with government departments. &#x2022; Provide evidenced-based policy advice. &#x2022; Conduct training for government officials on applying behavioral science. &#x2022; Disseminate CBS output and create advocacy for the communitiy development.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project initiated with DFID&apos;s support to establish a behavioural science unit with the University of Dar es salaam, Department of Economics. The unit aims at using behavioural science to improve the design and implementation of policies and interventions.</narrative>
  </description>
